[The total number of measles cases in the DRC since the beginning of 2019 (106 870), dwarfs the number of Ebola cases (2168), in spite of the number of vaccinations against measles (2 million in April 2019 alone). Both diseases are vaccine preventable, yet control of the outbreaks remains elusive. - Mod.LK

